2.love-2d-game-framework
jskyzero 2019/10/13


0. why learn love2d ?

唔，首先是學習框架本身，其次是關於如何設計一個框架，以及調用DLL等技巧性知識。


1. download love2d from https://love2d.org/

2. read the documents and have a try!

運行：
  love 2.love-2d-game-framework

3. framework
3.0 system execute sequence
3.1 scene structure
3.2 player move
3.3 scene element
3.4 clickable ui
3.5 mvc structure
3.6 basic game



